Several market players are actively involved in the CBD tea industry, with each contributing to the market through their unique product offerings and marketing strategies. The Tea Trove is known for its premium CBD-infused tea products that have gained popularity among health-conscious consumers. The Brothers Apothecary specializes in crafting artisanal CBD teas that combine the benefits of CBD with herbal blends for holistic wellness. Buddha Teas stands out for its diverse range of CBD tea flavors that cater to different taste preferences. The Hemp Garden focuses on providing high-quality CBD tea products sourced from organically grown hemp plants. Pure Science Lab is recognized for its innovative CBD tea formulations and commitment to product purity and potency. These market players play a significant role in driving market growth and shaping consumer perceptions of CBD tea products.

